NE\u201d TOPS AT 4syte TV Music Video Awards 2010|url=http://www.shout-africa.com/entertainment/ghana-4x4-%E2%80%9Cfresh-one%E2%80%9D-tops-at-4syte-tv-music-video-awards-2010/|publisher=Shout-Africa|accessdate=16 July 2014|date=22 November 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715063935/http://www.shout-africa.com/entertainment/ghana-4x4-%e2%80%9cfresh-one%e2%80%9d-tops-at-4syte-tv-music-video-awards-2010/|archive-date=15 July 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|Best Storyline Video\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Female Video\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best African Act Video\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Ghana Music Awards\n|Highlife Song of the Year\n|rowspan=\"2\"|\"Daa Ke Daa\"\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"GhanaNewsNow.com\">{{cite web|title=Ghana Music Awards nominees out, Sarkodie leads the pack|url=http://www.ghananewsnow.com/2010/03/02/ghana-music-awards-nominees-out-sarkodie-leads-the-pack/|publisher=GhanaNewsNow.com|accessdate=10 July 2014|date=2 March 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|Record of the Year\n|{{won}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mensah|first1=Nii|title=Ghana Music Awards 2010 winners|url=http://www.ghanamusic.com/news/top-stories/ghana-music-awards-2010-winners/index.html|publisher=Ghana Music.com|accessdate=10 July 2014|date=11 April 2010|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414101443/http://www.ghanamusic.com/news/top-stories/ghana-music-awards-2010-winners/index.html|archivedate=14 April 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|Best Female Vocal Performance\n|rowspan=\"6\"|Herself\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Artist of the Year\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"GhanaNewsNow.com\"/>\n|-\n|[[Kora Awards]]\n|Best African Prospect Award \n|{{won}}\n|<ref name=\"ghanameets\">{{cite web|title=Becca nominated for award in Nigeria|url=http://ghanameets.weebly.com/becca-nominated-for-award-in-nigeria.html|website=ghanameets.weebly.com|accessdate=5 July 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714163319/http://ghanameets.weebly.com/becca-nominated-for-award-in-nigeria.html|archive-da